1064
00:59:56,700 --> 00:59:58,960
 tad su bili Marija Selak i Nino Raspudić,

1065
00:59:58,960 --> 01:00:01,140
 bio je Jokić, Rada Borić,

1066
01:00:01,140 --> 01:00:02,040
 Sljevice i ja.

1067
01:00:02,040 --> 01:00:04,220
 A Marija je igrala neku tu ulogu,

1068
01:00:04,220 --> 01:00:05,520
 ono, kao neutralno,

1069
01:00:05,520 --> 01:00:06,900
 i sad smo bili ono kao Nino i ja,

1070
01:00:06,900 --> 01:00:09,720
 i Rada i Boris Jokić.

1071
01:00:09,720 --> 01:00:11,860
 I točno je bio onako dosta dobar

1072
01:00:11,860 --> 01:00:12,620
 i omjer snaga,

1073
01:00:12,620 --> 01:00:14,060
 i nekako,

1074
01:00:14,060 --> 01:00:17,220
 čak smo i privatno bili nekako dobri,

1075
01:00:17,360 --> 01:00:19,100
 iako je nakroju bio Jokić taj

1076
01:00:19,100 --> 01:00:23,120
