1139
01:01:44,240 --> 01:01:44,840
 na bitno netu,

1140
01:01:44,840 --> 01:01:45,240
 nedavno,

1141
01:01:45,240 --> 01:01:47,000
 dvije godine,

1142
01:01:47,000 --> 01:01:49,080
